query:
UPDATE
                transactions
            SET
                l1_batch_number = $3,
                l1_batch_tx_index = data_table.l1_batch_tx_index,
                updated_at = NOW()
            FROM
                (
                    SELECT
                        UNNEST($1 :: INT []) AS l1_batch_tx_index,
                        UNNEST($2 :: bytea []) AS hash
                ) AS data_table
            WHERE
                transactions.hash = data_table.hash
